item.title: Fabian Montes
item.description: Fabián Andrés Montes Tobar # Hola # Welcome to the gohugo template to create rich content academic reports having p5.js sketches. Quien Soy # Install the gohugo static site generator then: $git clone https://github.com/VisualComputing/showcase $cd showcase $git submodule update --init --recursive $hugo server -D --disableFastRender Deploy with $git push after redefined baseURL in config.toml which should point to your actual public remote. Don’t rename the repo but leave it as ‘showcase’
